Replace the existing SubagentPart schema, SubagentStartedEvent, SubagentProgressEvent, and SubagentDoneEvent in `packages/shared/src/schemas.ts` with the new BackgroundTask data model and corresponding SSE events. Also update `packages/shared/src/types.ts` to re-export the new types.

## Implementation

### 1. Update `packages/shared/src/schemas.ts`

Replace the SubagentPart and subagent event schemas:

