- Agent tasks: first click morphs the X icon to a "Stop?" text label; second click calls `onConfirm`
- The "Stop?" confirmation auto-dismisses after 3 seconds, reverting to the X icon
- The button is keyboard-accessible: Enter and Space trigger the click handler
- Focus-visible ring follows the design system pattern
- The confirmation state is styled with `destructive` color tokens
- Timer is properly cleaned up on unmount
- The button remains focusable while the "Stop?" label is visible

